                <!-- 10-Layer QC Overview -->
                <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-xl p-6 mb-8">
                    <h3 class="font-black text-brandBlue uppercase mb-4">Our 10-Layer Quality Control System</h3>
                    <ol class="text-slate-600 text-sm space-y-2 list-decimal list-inside">
                        <li><strong>IQC, Incoming Component Inspection</strong>: Cell grading, IC verification, material compliance</li>
                        <li><strong>IPQC, In-Process Monitoring</strong>: AOI, solder quality, coil alignment checks</li>
                        <li><strong>Stress Testing, Thermal</strong>: 4-hour full-load burn-in at 45°C ambient</li>
                        <li><strong>Stress Testing, Mechanical</strong>: Drop test (1.2m, 6 sides), vibration, salt spray</li>
                        <li><strong>Stress Testing, Electrical</strong>: Hi-pot, ESD immunity (8kV/15kV), output ripple</li>
                        <li><strong>Stress Testing, Safety</strong>: FOD detection, OVP/OCP/OTP triggers, short circuit</li>
                        <li><strong>FQC, Final Functional Test</strong>: Protocol handshake (PD 3.1, PPS, QC 5.0), charging speed</li>
                        <li><strong>Certification Verification</strong>: Cross-reference with UL/CE/FCC/UN38.3 test reports</li>
                        <li><strong>OQC, Outgoing Quality Check</strong>: Visual, packaging, labeling, barcode scan</li>
                        <li><strong>Traceability Logging</strong>: Unit-level test data archived for full batch recall capability</li>
                    </ol>
                </div>

                <!-- Quick Answer -->
                <div class="bg-brandBlue/5 border-l-4 border-brandOrange p-5 rounded-r-xl mb-8">
                    <p class="text-[11px] font-black text-brandOrange uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">QUICK ANSWER</p>
                    <p class="text-slate-700 text-sm"><strong>What defect rate should I expect from a quality charger factory?</strong> Industry standard AQL for consumer electronics is 0.65-1.0%. Premium OEM manufacturers like WOWOHCOOL maintain rates below 0.5% through 100% aging tests, AOI inspection, and comprehensive 4-stage QC systems (IQC, IPQC, FQC, OQC).</p>
                </div>

                <!-- Section 1: IQC -->
                <section id="section-iqc" class="mb-16">
                  <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-xl p-6 border border-slate-200 shadow-sm">
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-brandBlue uppercase italic mb-6">1. IQC: Grade A Cell & Component Selection</h2>
                    <div class="bg-brandBlue rounded-2xl p-8 text-white mb-8">
                        <p class="text-slate-300">Every component that enters our facility undergoes rigorous incoming inspection. We don't just buy batteries, we sort them to ensure 100% balance in our high-capacity packs.</p>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-6">
                        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-4 border border-slate-200">
                            <h4 class="font-black text-brandBlue uppercase mb-3"><svg class="icon-car-battery text-brandOrange mr-2" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false" viewBox="0 0 512 512">
    <path d="M80 64c0-17.7 14.3-32 32-32l64 0c17.7 0 32 14.3 32 32l96 0c0-17.7 14.3-32 32-32l64 0c17.7 0 32 14.3 32 32l16 0c35.3 0 64 28.7 64 64l0 256c0 35.3-28.7 64-64 64L64 448c-35.3 0-64-28.7-64-64L0 128C0 92.7 28.7 64 64 64l16 0zM392 184c0-13.3-10.7-24-24-24s-24 10.7-24 24l0 32-32 0c-13.3 0-24 10.7-24 24s10.7 24 24 24l32 0 0 32c0 13.3 10.7 24 24 24s24-10.7 24-24l0-32 32 0c13.3 0 24-10.7 24-24s-10.7-24-24-24l-32 0 0-32zM64 240c0 13.3 10.7 24 24 24l112 0c13.3 0 24-10.7 24-24s-10.7-24-24-24L88 216c-13.3 0-24 10.7-24 24z" fill="currentColor"/>
  </svg>Power Bank Cell Sorting</h4>
                            <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Every cell undergoes internal resistance (IR) testing and capacity grading. We match cells with identical performance profiles to ensure perfect balance in our high-capacity power banks.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-4 border border-slate-200">
                            <h4 class="font-black text-brandBlue uppercase mb-3"><svg class="icon-microchip text-brandOrange mr-2" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false" viewBox="0 0 512 512">
    <path d="M176 24c0-13.3-10.7-24-24-24s-24 10.7-24 24l0 40c-35.3 0-64 28.7-64 64l-40 0c-13.3 0-24 10.7-24 24s10.7 24 24 24l40 0 0 56-40 0c-13.3 0-24 10.7-24 24s10.7 24 24 24l40 0 0 56-40 0c-13.3 0-24 10.7-24 24s10.7 24 24 24l40 0c0 35.3 28.7 64 64 64l0 40c0 13.3 10.7 24 24 24s24-10.7 24-24l0-40 56 0 0 40c0 13.3 10.7 24 24 24s24-10.7 24-24l0-40 56 0 0 40c0 13.3 10.7 24 24 24s24-10.7 24-24l0-40c35.3 0 64-28.7 64-64l40 0c13.3 0 24-10.7 24-24s-10.7-24-24-24l-40 0 0-56 40 0c13.3 0 24-10.7 24-24s-10.7-24-24-24l-40 0 0-56 40 0c13.3 0 24-10.7 24-24s-10.7-24-24-24l-40 0c0-35.3-28.7-64-64-64l0-40c0-13.3-10.7-24-24-24s-24 10.7-24 24l0 40-56 0 0-40c0-13.3-10.7-24-24-24s-24 10.7-24 24l0 40-56 0 0-40zM160 128l192 0c17.7 0 32 14.3 32 32l0 192c0 17.7-14.3 32-32 32l-192 0c-17.7 0-32-14.3-32-32l0-192c0-17.7 14.3-32 32-32zm16 48l0 160 160 0 0-160-160 0z" fill="currentColor"/>
  </svg>GaN Chip Selection</h4>
                            <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Only Tier-1 GaN chips (Navitas, Innoscience, or equivalent) enter our SMT lines to guarantee thermal stability in high-wattage adapters.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="bg-brandBlue/5 border border-brandBlue/30 rounded-xl p-6">
                        <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm"><strong>Engineering Insight:</strong> Beware of factories that only do 'spot-checking' for aging tests. For high-density Power Banks and GaN chargers, 100% testing is the only way to ensure thermal safety. We provide full testing logs for every SKU.</p>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </section>

                <!-- Section 2: IPQC -->
                <section id="section-ipqc" class="mb-16">
                  <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-xl p-6 border border-slate-200 shadow-sm">
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-brandBlue uppercase italic mb-6">2. IPQC: Real-Time Production Monitoring</h2>
                    <div class="bg-brandBlue rounded-2xl p-8 text-white mb-8">
                        <p class="text-slate-300">After SMT assembly, every unit undergoes automated optical inspection (AOI) and in-process quality checks to catch defects before they become problems.</p>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-4 border border-slate-200 mb-6">
                        <h4 class="font-black text-brandBlue uppercase mb-3"><svg class="icon-crosshairs text-brandOrange mr-2" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false" viewBox="0 0 576 512">
    <path d="M288-16c17.7 0 32 14.3 32 32l0 18.3c98.1 14 175.7 91.6 189.7 189.7l18.3 0c17.7 0 32 14.3 32 32s-14.3 32-32 32l-18.3 0c-14 98.1-91.6 175.7-189.7 189.7l0 18.3c0 17.7-14.3 32-32 32s-32-14.3-32-32l0-18.3C157.9 463.7 80.3 386.1 66.3 288L48 288c-17.7 0-32-14.3-32-32s14.3-32 32-32l18.3 0C80.3 125.9 157.9 48.3 256 34.3L256 16c0-17.7 14.3-32 32-32zM131.2 288c12.7 62.7 62.1 112.1 124.8 124.8l0-12.8c0-17.7 14.3-32 32-32s32 14.3 32 32l0 12.8c62.7-12.7 112.1-62.1 124.8-124.8L432 288c-17.7 0-32-14.3-32-32s14.3-32 32-32l12.8 0C432.1 161.3 382.7 111.9 320 99.2l0 12.8c0 17.7-14.3 32-32 32s-32-14.3-32-32l0-12.8C193.3 111.9 143.9 161.3 131.2 224l12.8 0c17.7 0 32 14.3 32 32s-14.3 32-32 32l-12.8 0zM288 208a48 48 0 1 1 0 96 48 48 0 1 1 0-96z" fill="currentColor"/>
  </svg>Wireless Charger Coil Alignment</h4>
                        <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Precision coil alignment is verified by laser sensors to ensure maximum charging efficiency and 0% magnetic interference with the device.</p>
                    </div>
                    
